title: No. 8 Summit over No. 9 Immaculate Heart - Girls lacrosse recap (PHOTOS)
body: Girl's High School Lacrosse  Immaculate Heart Academy  Meets SummitKit Zanelli recorded four goals and six additional players marked the score sheet to lead Summit, No. 8 in the NJ.com Top 20, to a 17-6 win over No. 9 Immaculate Heart in Summit.Lily Spinner and Jane Freeman recorded a hat trick each for Summit and Freeman added two assists. Lauren Riley had two goals and an assist and Ashley Thomas and Maggie DeFabio each recorded two goals.Brooke Marotti led Immaculate Heart with three goals.Note to readers: if you purchase something through one of our affiliate links we may earn a commission.
